OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FA knife attack in Golders Green in
OL,7,FLondon left two men wounded, sent
OL,8,Fshockwaves through the Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity, and intensified calls for
OL,10,Furgent government action on
OL,11,Fantisemitism.
OL,13,FThe attack, which only lasted 15
OL,14,Fminutes, saw two Jewish men ` 34-year-
OL,15,Fold Shloime Rand and 76-year-old Moshe
OL,16,FBen Baila, named locally as Moshe
OL,17,FShine ` taken to hospital. Both are
OL,18,Fexpected to make a full recovery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
