OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FA 45-year-old man, said by police to
OL,7,Fbe a Somali-born British national, was
OL,8,Farrested following the incident on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FThe stabbings are the latest in a
OL,12,Fseries of attacks on Jewish sites over
OL,13,Frecent weeks and have prompted calls
OL,14,Ffor urgent action and accusations that
OL,15,Fthe government has not done enough to
OL,16,Ftackle antisemitism.
OL,18,FHere, ITV News looks at how the attack
OL,19,Funfolded.
OL,21,FIncident in south-east London
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
