OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FCCTV footage appears to show the
OL,7,Fsuspect jogging along the road,
OL,8,Fapproaching Mr Rand, who is walking
OL,9,Ftowards him.
OL,11,FAbove: Suspect lunges at a man in the
OL,12,Fstreet who manages to escape
OL,14,FThe suspect then lunges at Mr Rand,
OL,15,Fbut he manages to escape and runs
OL,16,Ftoward Golders Green Road while
OL,17,Fcalling for help.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
