OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FMr Rand told ITV News that he had just
OL,7,Fleft his local synagogue and was on
OL,8,Fhis way to work, when he was stabbed
OL,9,Fin the chest.
OL,11,FHe said: "This fellow came towards me
OL,12,Fand just stabbed me in the chest... I
OL,13,Fjumped back, so thankfully it was only
OL,14,Fone stab. It could have taken my life."
OL,16,FPolice said they received the first
OL,17,Freport about a stabbing on Highfield
OL,18,FAvenue at 11.16am.
OL,20,FSuspect carries out second attack at a
OL,21,Fbus stop on Golders Green Road
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
