OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FMore CCTV footage shows the suspect
OL,7,Fwalking towards a bus stop at 11.20am
OL,8,Fon Golders Green Road, just north of
OL,9,Fthe location of the first attack.
OL,11,FAs he approaches the bus stop, he
OL,12,Fappears to pull out a knife and lunges
OL,13,Fat Mr Baila, who was waiting at the
OL,14,Fbus stop and stabs him.
OL,16,FAbove: A moment the suspected knifeman
OL,17,Fattacks a victim at a bus stop
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
