OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FThe Daily Mail reported Mr Balia was
OL,7,Fstabbed at least twice and sought help
OL,8,Ffrom a pizza shop nearby, where
OL,9,Fmembers of staff tried to support him.
OL,11,FSuspect seen running and lunging at
OL,12,Fpeople
OL,14,FSoon after the attack on Mr Balia,
OL,15,Ffootage captured from a car shows the
OL,16,Fsuspect running up the road.
OL,18,FThe passengers in the car are yelling
OL,19,Fat other people on the road as they
OL,20,Fsound their horn, alerting them of the
OL,21,Fdanger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
