OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FAbove: The suspect is seen running up
OL,7,Fthe road, lunging at people
OL,9,FSeveral people are seen leaping out of
OL,10,Fthe path of the attacker, who has a
OL,11,Fknife in his hand.
OL,13,FSuspect tasered and arrested by police
OL,15,FAt 11.29am the suspect has moved
OL,16,Ffurther north up Golders Green Road,
OL,17,Fwhere police have caught up with him.
OL,19,FAbove: Moment the suspect is tasered
OL,20,Fby police in north London
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
