OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FA confrontation between two police
OL,7,Fofficers and the suspect begins when
OL,8,Fthe officers yell at him to stop
OL,9,Fbefore the suspect pulls a knife out
OL,10,Fof his pocket.
OL,12,FWithin 20 seconds of the knife being
OL,13,Fdrawn, the police have tasered the
OL,14,Fsuspect.
OL,16,FThe two officers and a member of the
OL,17,Fpublic then demand that he drop the
OL,18,Fknife as the suspect lies on the floor
OL,19,Fwith the knife in his hand beneath him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
