PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777583466
OL,3,CHow the Golders Green terror attack
OL,4,Cunfolded
OL,6,FBoth officers kick the suspect several
OL,7,Ftimes, with some of the blows landing
OL,8,Fon his head, as they attempt to disarm
OL,9,Fthe suspect.
OL,11,FAbove: the moment the suspect is
OL,12,Farrested. (Video credit: X @N12NEWS)
OL,14,FAn officer and the member of the
OL,15,Fpublic eventually manage to get the
OL,16,Fsuspect's arm out from beneath him,
OL,17,Fand the knife is taken out of his hand.
OL,19,FThe officers then handcuff the suspect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
